{"tid":1166311,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"鈄路入波”嘭”一聲","createTime":"2019-05-22T10:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T07:42:32.000Z","uid":35693,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d59a213fef380c5c6fa88050a4a891d742d97aab","tid":1166311,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"我架係cvt自動波車<br />\n無手制拉，得電子手制<br />\n平時都好少泊係鈄路<br />\n<br />\n今日擺左係鈄路<br />\n到我攞車閃人果陣，<br />\n踩住迫力由p波落r波果陣<br />\n聽到好大聲&rdquo;嘭&rdquo;一聲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚇到我鳩都縮埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我又尊登轉一轉位又試多次<br />\n又係&rdquo;嘭&rdquo;一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後發覺係鈄路先會有聲<br />\n平路係正常無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打知發生咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲下返廠check車順便都要問下佢咩事<br />\n叫佢check下波箱先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚肉赤"},{"pid":"abb6c662e9529416e4a26e62d48b58077d29c1ea","tid":1166311,"uid":59001,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"入錯racing波"},{"pid":"f02a1b32f1ea6d83584a4fd6a2528897355da156","tid":1166311,"uid":34910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"有無用hand brake?"},{"pid":"f0787ce782eb1d6aa67db101ff6e850a912d9cb9","tid":1166311,"uid":35693,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f02a1b32f1ea6d83584a4fd6a2528897355da156","tid":1166311,"uid":34910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"有無用hand brake?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T10:51:46.000Z","msg":"有關係架？<img s